messages.content: Don't make assumptions about what values to plug into functions. Ask for clarification if a user request is ambiguous.
The guy at +12453344098, I feel like we don't talk much anymore. Get him out of my contacts.
Could you please provide the person_id of the contact you want to remove? This will help me identify the correct contact in your database.
I don't have any other info, just the phone number, +12453344098.

I understand you'd like to remove the contact with the phone number +12453344098, but I need the person_id to proceed. Could you check your contact list for this number and provide the associated person_id?
I don't have access to any person_id. I only know the phone number.

I see. Unfortunately, I can't remove a contact without knowing the person_id. You may need to review your contact list to find the person_id associated with the phone number +12453344098. Once you have it, I can help you remove the contact.
